    "body": "## Steps to reproduce\r\n1. Go to Settings -> General -> Language, and change to a different language than the default/the one selected.\r\n2. Exit settings and observe that the carousel tips are not translated.\r\n\r\n### Expected behavior\r\n Focus displays every UI text in the new language, including the carousel tips, immediately after changing the language.\r\n\r\n### Actual behavior\r\nThe carousel tips remain displayed in the default/previously set language and are only updated after restarting the application. \r\n\r\n### Device information\r\n* Android device: Huawei P9 Lite (Android 8), Huawei P20 (Android 10).\r\n* Focus version: 93.0 (Build 352452037 ; 93.0a1-20210831093704).\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/89388888/131998676-d132e6d4-76ef-4ab4-8c2d-2aa5ba2ca68c.mp4\r\n",
